<li>You don't want to learn Webflow</li>
<li>You need built-in e-commerce</li>
<li>You prefer templates over AI generation</li>
<li>You're not a designer/developer</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="p-6 bg-purple-50 border-l-4 border-purple-500">
<h3>Choose Relume If:</h3>
<ul class="list-disc pl-6">
<li>You already use Webflow</li>
<li>You want complete design control</li>
<li>You're a designer or developer</li>
<li>You need custom functionality</li>
<li>You value speed + flexibility</li>
</ul>
</div>
